output:
Map {
User Stories {
  Display Unsupported Orders: As a user, I want to be able to view all orders that are not supported by the Fantasy Sports application.

Select Travel Time: As a user, I want to be able to select a travel time for my fantasy sports team.

Create Fantasy Team: As a user, I want to be able to create a fantasy team with players from different sports.

View Player Stats: As a user, I want to be able to view the stats of each player on my fantasy team.

Manage Fantasy Team: As a user, I want to be able to manage my fantasy team by adding, removing, and trading players.

View League Standings: As a user, I want to be able to view the standings of my fantasy league.

View Team History: As a user, I want to be able to view the history of my fantasy team.

Create Fantasy League: As a user, I want to be able to create a fantasy league with other users.

Invite Friends: As a user, I want to be able to invite my friends to join my fantasy league.

View Leaderboard: As a user, I want to be able to view the leaderboard of my fantasy league.

View Matchups: As a user, I want to be able to view the matchups of my fantasy league.

View Schedules: As a user, I want to be able to view the schedules of my fantasy league.

View Transactions: As a user, I want to be able to view the transactions of my fantasy league.

Chat with Other Users: As a user, I want to be able to chat with other users in my fantasy league.

View News Feed: As a user, I want to be able to view the news feed of my fantasy league.

}
}
